These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
House: cape-cod, palace, craftsman
1. House:palace is on the right of House:craftsman##1
2. House:cape-cod is on the far right##1
3. House:cape-cod is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| House   | craftsman | palace | cape-cod |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Birthday: april, december, february
1. Birthday:december is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:april is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Birthday   | april | february | december |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: folk, punk, disco
1. Music-Genre:punk is in an even position##4
2. Music-Genre:punk is on the left or right of Music-Genre:disco##3
3. Music-Genre:disco is on the right of Music-Genre:punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Music-Genre   | folk | punk | disco |

 #################################
 
